= Choose a Lübeck coalition

A coalition is selectable if it controls at least **41** of the **80** seats. If no listed coalition has a majority, the incumbent Lübeck government may continue as a minority cabinet.

- @lubeck_select_spd_ddp
- @lubeck_select_spd_ddp_dvp
- @lubeck_select_ddp_dvp_hvb
- @lubeck_select_ddp_dvp_dnvp_hvb
- @lubeck_select_dvp_dnvp_nsdap
- @new_lubeck_elections: Call new Lübeck elections.
- @root: Continue without changing the Lübeck government.

